d altre PA.</p>\n<p>In bocca al lupo a Giuseppe e <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/nazzareno.prinzivalli\">Nazzareno Prinzivalli</a> (e a tutte le persone coinvolte).</p>\n<h3 id=\"letteraemme-un-altro-tipo-di-giornalismo\">‚Äúletteraemme‚Äù, un altro tipo di giornalismo</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/letteraemme_\"><div data-gatsby-image-wrapper=\"\" style=\"position:relative;overflow:hidden;display:inline-block;vertical-align:top\" class=\"gatsby-image-wrapper gatsby-image-wrapper-constrained alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-1509 inline-gatsby-image-wrapper\" data-reactroot=\"\"><div style=\"max-width:150px;display:block\"><img alt=\"\" role=\"presentation\" aria-hidden=\"true\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;charset=utf-8,%3Csvg height=&#x27;150&#x27; width=&#x27;150&#x27; xmlns=&#x27;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#x27; version=&#x27;1.1&#x27;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" style=\"max-width:100%;display:block;position:static\"/></div><div aria-hidden=\"true\" data-placeholder-image=\"\" style=\"height:100%;left:0;position:absolute;top:0;width:100%\"></div><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" data-srcset=\"/static/99709ae9af6cc2e666c155ed56afbf3b/7c74d/tfM5ARHw_400x400.webp 38w,/static/99709ae9af6cc2e666c155ed56afbf3b/7572c/tfM5ARHw_400x400.webp 75w,/static/99709ae9af6cc2e666c155ed56afbf3b/4bee1/tfM5ARHw_400x400.webp 150w,/static/99709ae9af6cc2e666c155ed56afbf3b/78de2/tfM5ARHw_400x400.webp 300w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 150px) 150px, 100vw\"/><img data-gatsby-image-ssr=\"\" data-wp-inline-image=\"3\" data-main-image=\"\" style=\"height:100%;left:0;position:absolute;top:0;transform:translateZ(0);transition:opacity 250ms linear;width:100%;will-change:opacity;opacity:0\" sizes=\"(min-width: 150px) 150px, 100vw\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" data-src=\"/static/99709ae9af6cc2e666c155ed56afbf3b/db3a2/tfM5ARHw_400x400.jpg\" data-srcset=\"/static/99709ae9af6cc2e666c155ed56afbf3b/103ed/tfM5ARHw_400x400.jpg 38w,/static/99709ae9af6cc2e666c155ed56afbf3b/61e88/tfM5ARHw_400x400.jpg 75w,